<CONTROL>


[Method]
Dir
[Function]
dcl_ComboBox_Dir
[Desc]
This method will fill the ComboBox with a list of files found in the directory search that matches the \cf1 sExtension \cf0 argument.  If the \cf1 sExtension \cf0 is not specified *.* is assumed.
[Arguments]
<CONTROL>
\par\tab sDirectory
[as String]
\par\tab\i{Optional} \i0 sExtension
[as String]


[Method]
GetDir
[Function]
dcl_ComboBox_GetDir
[Desc]
This method will retrieve the currently selected directory of the directory combo box.
[Arguments]
<CONTROL>


