<CONTROL>


[Method]
SetCurSel
[Function]
dcl_ComboBox_SetCurSel
[Desc]
This method will set the currently selected list item in a single selection ComboBox. Pass in a -1 if you wish to deselect the current selection.
[Arguments]
<CONTROL>
\par\tab nIndex
[as Integer]


[Method]
GetCurSel
[Function]
dcl_ComboBox_GetCurSel
[Desc]
This method will return the index of the currently selected list item in a single selection ComboBox. -1 will be returned if nothing is selected.
[Arguments Return] as Integer
<CONTROL>


